7 (j) Notwithstanding any provision of this section to the contrary, the following
8 provisions apply to a local board of education that contracts with a person under G.S. 115C-253
9 to provide transportation services to students:
10 (1) The local board of education shall require an individual to submit to a criminal
11 history check before allowing that individual to act as a driver pursuant to a
